title: BRIEF-Guangdong Qtone Education gets regulatory approval to acquire assets
text:
BRIEF-Guangdong Qtone Education gets regulatory approval to acquire assets Sept 16 
Sept 16 Guangdong Qtone Education Co Ltd 
* Says gets regulatory approval to acquire assets, trading of shares to resume on Sept 17
